<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 12</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line-white: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--white);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--green);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Decorative Background */
    .bg-mark {
      position: absolute;
      right: -16mm;
      bottom: -22mm;
      font-size: 155px;
      line-height: 0.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.08em;
      font-weight: 780;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      pointer-events: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .bg-line {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      top: 58mm;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 24mm;
      height: 128mm;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 10mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.075em;
      font-weight: 780;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 14mm;
      max-width: 138mm;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .closing-note {
      margin-top: 10mm;
      width: 108mm;
      padding-top: 6mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Contact Panel */
    .contact-panel {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8mm;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-white);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    }

    .panel-label {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 12mm;
    }

    .contact-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .contact-table th,
    .contact-table td {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
      padding: 4.3mm 0;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .contact-table th {
      width: 28mm;
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .contact-table td {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .contact-message {
      margin-top: 10mm;
      padding-top: 6mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    }

    .contact-message-title {
      margin: 0 0 4mm;
      font-size: 21px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 780;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .contact-message-text {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.8px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 2;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <div class="bg-line"></div>
    <div class="bg-mark">Taepyung</div>

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 흰색 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-white.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Thank You</div>

          <h1>
            정직한 품질로<br />
            더 나은 일상을<br />
            만들어갑니다
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 오랜 제조 경험과 안정적인 생산 시스템을 바탕으로
            생활에 필요한 위생 제품을 꾸준히 공급해왔습니다.
            앞으로도 고객의 일상 가까이에서 신뢰할 수 있는 제품을 만들어가겠습니다.
          </p>

          <div class="closing-note">
            생활 위생지 제조와 유통, 브랜드 운영 경험을 기반으로
            고객과 시장이 필요로 하는 제품을 안정적으로 공급하는 기업이 되겠습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="contact-panel">
          <div class="panel-label">Contact Information</div>

          <table class="contact-table">
            <tr>
              <th>Company</th>
              <td>태평제지</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Brand</th>
              <td>브론디 blondy</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Address</th>
              <td>경기도 이천시 마장면 마도로 223번길 22</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Website</th>
              <td>www.blondy.co.kr</td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <div class="contact-message">
            <h3 class="contact-message-title">
              Everyday Trust,<br />
              Honest Quality.
            </h3>

            <p class="contact-message-text">
              고객의 일상 가까이에 놓이는 제품일수록
              더 정직한 품질과 안정적인 공급이 필요하다고 믿습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">12</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
